the cost of sched_move_task:

  bpftrace -e 'k:sched_move_task { @ts[tid] = nsecs; }
	       kr:sched_move_task /@ts[tid]/
		  { @ns += nsecs - @ts[tid]; delete(@ts[tid]); }'

